title: [Discussion] Shrinkflation is Moving in. 1.6 ounce two pack is down to 1.5 ounces. #shrinkflation

[Discussion] Some Say Low Interest Rates Cause Inequality. What if It’s the Reverse? The Federal Reserve’s low interest rate policies and other steps meant to boost the economy are driving the value of stocks and other assets to the moon, and thus are a major cause of high wealth inequality.
